S&P 500 Stocks Biggest Weekly Changes in Target Price

-- B y   W e n d y   S o o n g
-- 
2011-09-30T17:28:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/s-p-500-stocks-biggest-weekly-changes-in-target-price.html
The following tables show the biggest
increases and decreases in analysts’ target price, according to Bloomberg
data, for companies in the Standard & Poor’s 500 Index from Sept. 23.  The average target price reflects forecasts for the next 12 months,
a period that varies among brokerage firms. The ratings are averaged
from the analysts’ recommendations made during the past 12 months with 5
being the highest recommendation.  
